title: DDFP 238: Best QB-RB duos & mock draft
itunes:title: DDFP 238: Best QB-RB duos & mock draft
description:
Shek, Rank, Handsome Hank & Elliot Harrison debate the best quarterback-running back pairing in the NFL and take part in the first-ever live #DDFP mock draft. Also, Shek and E.H. share their thoughts on the greatest quarterback in Green Bay Packers history. Lastly, Shek & Hank have a "True Detective" discussion leading up to the season finale of the HBO series (**SPOILER ALERT** at 1:25:20). 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
